events.name: ◇追い詰められイベント続き

parameters:
\SE[3]That's right... This is a matter of state affairs. If
you resist, you will lose your graduation qualification and
the rights to your family name. \SE[36]I recommend
surrendering obediently...

\SE[33]Both of those... \SE[3]It doesn't matter to me.
\SE[3]Compared to my precious homeland, it's nothing.
\SE[0]...I thought so. \SE[3]It was a pointless exchange.

\SE[0]There is no such thing as a pointless matter...
\SE[3]Being able to recognize my enemy... \SE[0]I believe it
was a very meaningful dialogue.
...This is not the time to turn back.
